{"tid":2510833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府上財年錄得赤字2325億元","createTime":"2021-04-30T12:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T12:19:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"880551e30702eb4b2e6fd1a25c51f5c65306ba09","tid":2510833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588641-20210430.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588641-20210430.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=913833e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588641-20210430.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5dfaa48f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588641-20210430.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府公布上個財政年度臨時財政數字。<br />\n<br />\n政府在2020至2021年整體開支8160億港元，收入5642億元，計入政府綠色債券計劃下發行的綠色債券所得淨收入193億元後，該個財年有2325億赤字。   <br />\n<br />\n政府指，綜合赤字較修訂預算2576億元，減少251億元。其中收入比預測增加3.8%，由於印花稅、入息及利得稅收入比預期高，而開支需要較預期少，令開支較修訂預算減少0.5%。<br />\n<br />\n政府又指，臨時數字與原來預算的差異，包括開支增加11.6%，收入減少1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，所有數字均為臨時數字，有待年度帳目最後結算作實。不過根據經驗，即使臨時數字有變動，幅度也不會很大。"},{"pid":"1edebfdd1c9057fd24415faaa90bc0e18cd0a9c0","tid":2510833,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}